"[path]``/usr/share/rhn/config-defaults/rhn_java_sso.conf``에서 사용자 정의할 "
"파라미터를 찾습니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso.adoc:37
msgid ""
"Insert the parameters you want to customize into [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` "
"and prefix them with [literal]``java.sso``.  For example, in [path]``/usr/"
"share/rhn/config-defaults/rhn_java_sso.conf`` find:"
