"On SLES{nbsp}12 systems, live patching is managed by kGraft.  For in depth "
"information covering kGraft use, see https://documentation.suse.com/sles/12-"
"SP5/html/SLES-all/cha-kgraft.html."
msgstr ""
"SLES{nbsp}12 시스템에서 라이브 패치는 kGraft에서 관리합니다. kGraft 사용에 대"
"한 자세한 내용은 link:https://documentation.suse.com/sles/12-SP5/html/SLES-"
"all/cha-kgraft.html[]을 참조하십시오."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/live-patching-sles12.adoc:3
#: modules/administration/pages/live-patching-sles15.adoc:3
msgid "Before you begin, ensure:"
