msgstr "필요에 따라 기타 구성 옵션을 사용자 정의합니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:38
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:67
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:152
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:181
msgid "Click btn:[Save Formula]."
msgstr "btn:[수식 저장]을 클릭합니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:39
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:68
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:182
msgid "Apply the highstate and confirm that it completes successfully."
