#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:40
msgid ""
"Check that the Prometheus interface loads correctly. In your browser, "
"navigate to the URL of the server where Prometheus is installed, on "
"port 9090 (for example, [literal]``http://example.com:9090``)."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 인터페이스를 올바르게 로드했는지 확인합니다. 브라우저에서 9090 포"
"트 Prometheus가 설치된 서버의 URL(예: [literal]``http://example.com:9090``)"
"로 이동합니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:41
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:91
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:155
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:183
msgid ""
"For more information about the monitoring formulas, see xref:specialized-"
"guides:salt/salt-formula-monitoring.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"수식 모니터링에 대한 자세한 내용은 xref:specialized-guides:salt/salt-formula-"
