#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:179
msgid "For example, ``9999``."
msgstr "예를 들어, ``9999``입니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:180
msgid "Customize the other exporters according to your needs."
msgstr "필요에 따라, 다른 엑스포트를 사용자 정의합니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:185
msgid ""
"Prometheus server and Prometheus node exporter offer a built-in mechanism to "
"secure their endpoints with TLS encryption and authentication.  "
