#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:190
msgid ""
"By default, {productname} does not provide any certificates for securing "
"monitoring configuration.  For providing security, you can generate or "
"import custom certificates, self-signed or signed by a third party "
"certificate authority (CA)."
