#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Renewing GPG Key"
msgstr "GPG 키 갱신"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:14
msgid ""
"If you want to renew a GPG key, first remove the old key, and then generate "
"and import a new one."
msgstr ""
"GPG 키를 갱신하려면 먼저 이전 키를 제거한 후 새 키를 생성하여 임포트합니다."

